sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Operator as Operator Manager<br/>ServiceAccount Token Auth
    participant Router as OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant OAuthProxy as OAuth Proxy<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant OAuthServer as OpenShift OAuth Server<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant TrustyAI as TrustyAI Service<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant PV as Persistent Volume<br/>Filesystem
    participant Prometheus as Prometheus<br/>Metrics Scraper
    participant InferenceService as InferenceService Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP

    Note over User,PV: Flow 1: TrustyAI Service Deployment

    User->>K8sAPI: kubectl apply TrustyAIService CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>kubeconfig credentials
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: Watch event (CR created)
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create PVC<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Service<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create Route<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Create ServiceMonitor<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token

    Note over User,PV: Flow 2: External Access to TrustyAI Service

    User->>Router: HTTPS Request to TrustyAI<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    Router->>OAuthProxy: Forward (TLS Passthrough)<br/>8443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    OAuthProxy->>OAuthServer: OAuth Redirect<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    OAuthServer-->>OAuthProxy: OAuth Token
    OAuthProxy->>K8sAPI: SubjectAccessReview (SAR)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>OAuthProxy: Authorization Decision
    OAuthProxy->>TrustyAI: Proxied Request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>localhost trust
    TrustyAI->>PV: Read/Write Data<br/>Filesystem, Pod UID/GID
    TrustyAI-->>OAuthProxy: Response
    OAuthProxy-->>Router: HTTPS Response
    Router-->>User: HTTPS Response

    Note over User,PV: Flow 3: Metrics Collection

    Prometheus->>TrustyAI: Scrape /q/metrics<br/>80/TCP HTTP via Service<br/>No Auth (skip-auth-regex)
    TrustyAI-->>Prometheus: Metrics Data (trustyai_spd, trustyai_dir)
    Prometheus->>Operator: Scrape /metrics<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>Bearer Token

    Note over User,PV: Flow 4: InferenceService Monitoring

    Operator->>K8sAPI: Watch InferenceService CRs<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    K8sAPI-->>Operator: InferenceService Event
    Operator->>K8sAPI: Patch Deployment (env vars)<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+<br/>ServiceAccount Token
    InferenceService->>TrustyAI: Send Inference Data<br/>8080/TCP HTTP<br/>No Auth
    TrustyAI->>PV: Store Inference Data<br/>Filesystem
